author: Barbara Nadene
comment: Awesome app! Very well thought out videos that goes at a pace that is just perfect. Challenging but not over the top! Soaking swear after each completed workout. Love that I can take a sweaty selfie immediately after it tells me how much calories I just burned and what it is equal to. Today I burned the equivalent of a scoop of vanilla. :)

author: John Johnson
comment: Main issues is it doesn't do half the things it says.  Doesn't log my workout,  dosent log goals,  won't let you add weights to your work outs, gives ludicrously low numbers for calories burned, doesn't count reps using a smart watch on the list. I do like the exercises,  but the not logging my work puts is really starting to get to me. I want to love this app but it's performance is making that hard

reply.author: Track My Fitness
reply.content: Could you please try uninstall, then reinstall, and let us know if the problem persists?
